claim.claim-text:
1. An information processing system comprising: 
a plurality of storages for storing information; 
one or more controllers for writing information in or reading information from said storages; 
location management means for locating a location of information stored in said storages; 
information duplication means for duplicating information between said storages; 
attribute preservation means for preserving attribute control representing an attribute of each of said storages; and 
wherein in a case said controllers write information in said storages or read information from said storages, said controllers perform the writing or reading process on the basis of the location information indicated by said location management means; and 
wherein said location management means manages the location of the information to be written in said storages by said controllers or the written information.
